OL,3,C'I lost 7.5 stone after my Covid video
OL,4,Cwent viral'
OL,6,FOne of the country's first Covid
OL,7,Fpatients said seeing herself after a
OL,8,Fvideo she posted from hospital went
OL,9,Fviral prompted her to change her life.
OL,11,FSharon Cook, an NHS worker, was
OL,12,Fadmitted to Lincoln County Hospital on
OL,13,Fthe day the country was placed into
OL,14,Flockdown exactly five years ago.
OL,16,FIn a video from her hospital bed she
OL,17,Fbegged people to stay at home, saying:
OL,18,F''If there had been an injection to
OL,19,Fput me down, I'd have taken it.''
