OL,3,C'I lost 7.5 stone after my Covid video
OL,4,Cwent viral'
OL,6,FThe video was viewed millions of times
OL,7,Fby people around the world.
OL,9,FBut on the fifth anniversary of
OL,10,Frestrictions, Sharon, of Cherry
OL,11,FWillingham, Lincolnshire, says she is
OL,12,F"fitter than ever" - and lockdown even
OL,13,Fprompted her to lose seven-and-a-half
OL,14,Fstone.
OL,16,FShe said: "When we were first allowed
OL,17,Fout, someone uploaded a photo of me to
OL,18,FFacebook and I thought, who is that?
OL,19,FThen I saw it was me and I was gutted.
OL,20,FSo I decided to make a change.''
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
