OL,3,C'I lost 7.5 stone after my Covid video
OL,4,Cwent viral'
OL,6,FPrime Minister Boris Johnson announced
OL,7,Fthe first lockdown of the pandemic on
OL,8,F23 March 2020 in an effort to curb the
OL,9,Fspread of Covid-19.
OL,11,FHe ordered people to "stay at home",
OL,12,Fwith major restrictions on movement to
OL,13,Flimit contact between people.
OL,15,FMs Cook had already developed serious
OL,16,Frespiratory problems and was taken to
OL,17,Fhospital to be ventilated.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
