OL,3,C'I lost 7.5 stone after my Covid video
OL,4,Cwent viral'
OL,6,FShe said: ''At the time it was
OL,7,Fpetrifying. The staff were scared as
OL,8,Fwell, quite rightly. They took me out
OL,9,Fof that room and put me on a trolley,
OL,10,Fshouting 'covid patient' and sort of
OL,11,Fpinning themselves against the wall.
OL,13,F''It all seems so surreal now. I can't
OL,14,Fbelieve that video is me. After I
OL,15,Fshared it the views just went up and
OL,16,Fup. And then I felt it was a
OL,17,Fresponsibility - had I been
OL,18,Fscaremongering?
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
