OL,3,C'I lost 7.5 stone after my Covid video
OL,4,Cwent viral'
OL,6,F"But I felt it wasn't worth going out
OL,7,Fand having fun for a couple of hours
OL,8,Fand ending up in hospital."
OL,10,FM Cook believes lockdown measures
OL,11,Fsaved lives - and were inevitable
OL,12,Fbecause "nobody understood the virus".
OL,14,FBut she said her own experience was a
OL,15,Fcatalyst for her to change her life
OL,16,Ffor the better.
