OL,3,C'I lost 7.5 stone after my Covid video
OL,4,Cwent viral'
OL,6,F''Fast forward to now and I don't look
OL,7,Fanything like I did then," she said.
OL,8,F"I wasn't fit (before catching
OL,9,Fcoronavirus) and that didn't help
OL,10,Frecovery. But it was actually as
OL,11,Flockdown ended that I really decided
OL,12,Fto make a change.
