OL,3,C'I lost 7.5 stone after my Covid video
OL,4,Cwent viral'
OL,6,F''The vaccination definitely helped.
OL,7,FBut I think people who didn't have it
OL,8,Fwere frowned upon, you'd go on
OL,9,Ffacebook and people would put on their
OL,10,Fprofile 'I've been vaccinated' - and
OL,11,Ffor people who didn't want to or
OL,12,Fdidn't agree with it - it's their
OL,13,Fchoice. It's your own choice with any
OL,14,Fvaccination.''
